  <thing id="cPWMyrmMoA" name="Deed: Man of Action" description="At 11th level, when the gunslinger hits a living creature with a firearm attack, she can spend 1 grit point as a free action to have that attack deal extra bleed damage. The amount of bleed damage is equal to the gunslinger&apos;s Dexterity modifier. Alternatively, the gunslinger can spend 2 grit points to deal 1 point of Strength, Dexterity, or Constitution bleed damage (gunslinger&apos;s choice) instead. Creatures that are immune to sneak attacks are also immune to these types of bleed damage." compset="ClSpecial" summary="Use 1 grit to gain circumstance nonus to Acrobatics, Climb or Swim checks">
